.TP 
\fBEIO\fR An I/O error occurred.

See \fBclose\fR(2) for additional details.
.SH "NOTE"
This function actually wraps the \fBclose\fR(2) routine.
.SH "CONFORMING TO"
ATC API SRS v02.05, August 11, 2006
.SH "RESTRICTIONS"
None.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBopen\fR(2),
\fBclose\fR(2),
\fBfpui_open\fR(3ite),
.bp
